          "Main Menu(Setting)",
          "Settings(Main Menu)",
          "Picture ( SDR 時)",
          "Preset Mode",
          "Standard"
        ]
      },
      "description": "Ensure Picture Mode is set to Standard before HDR pattern display."
    },
    {
